Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Helene and Gustav to tape\N"Detective Forster."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It re-airs on Tuesday at 10 AM.\NYou've never seen it? It's amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Milch, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time\Nto be joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.85,0:00:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how much\Ntrouble you've given our boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,screwing up and\Ngetting caught like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He retained me as your lawyer\Neven though you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,At least thank him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent you watch over me\Nso I don't say anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Milch, you know what's going\Nto happen if you tell the truth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NI'll never sell out my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Just file a confession\Nthat matches my scenario. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, has my next job\Nbeen scheduled?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Next? When do you think that'll be?\NThink about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Gunter Milch,\Nthe king of prison escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time for\Nyour silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, if you give them\Nthe confession I made up for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get out in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, tell Helene and Gustav\Nto tape "Detective Forster."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. But I can't really\Ncount on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm here in this police station,\NI guess I'll try it out once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Try what out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\Nhe's faking it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was blood in his vomit\Nand his body is so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. You came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,– Huh?\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Some young folks we brought in\Nwere getting rowdy on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Several people were injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But.. .he looks like\Nhe's going to die right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Milch again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him rest in the back.\NI'll take a look at him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then take me to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back immediately,\Nso wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly. People just keep\Nbringing patients to me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving me the bed\Nnext to a serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This man collapsed from starvation.\NHe's receiving an intravenous drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel even worse\Nbeing next to this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How many injured are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know\Nuntil we go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids won't\Nget away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What we talked\Nabout the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of killing\Nyour former fiancée...Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think\Nthat's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On that rainy day, she heard three gunshots\Nin that building that was under construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She... Eva won't\Ntestify about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants me to spend\Nthe rest of my life in jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wants me to spend the rest\Nof my life regretting that I dumped her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll only testify against me.\NSo... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I'm asking you\Nwhether you think it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's gone,\Nyou may not have to go to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Her death is advantageous\Nfor the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wii you tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wii you tell Verdemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be one of\Nmy comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're brilliant lawyers.\NWe'll find a way to clear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you finally get out,\Nyou can have a good drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, by that time, that arrogant, noisy,\Nruined woman will no longer be in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to sleep\Nnext to this murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Milch, keep to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep quiet or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to confess and\Nbe escorted to jail in five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to bid farewell\Nto murderers like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Nyammering on about, Milch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!\NYou really were faking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to put up with being with\Nthis murderer for five more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In five days...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,On that rainy day, you heard three\Ngunshots in a building under construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw a blond young man\Ncome down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:08:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you continue working on this\Ncase while ignoring Johan's existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Eva Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be willing to make\Nthis important testimony in court?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world does Dr. Tenma\Nwant so late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he have to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well... Anyway,\Nhe said to call an interrogator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to tell us,\NDr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dusseldorf's Eisler Memorial\NHospital's Director Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief of Surgery Dr. Oppenheim,\NDr. Boyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And my patient,\NAdolf Junkers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind blew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The bottle fell over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The sandwiches were\Ncovered in dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,he smiled sadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to the police announcement,\Non the fourth before dawn,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenzo Tenma, who had been\Ndenying all accusations{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of involvement in\Nthe multiple homicides until now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}suddenly gave a complete confession\Nof the murders of the director and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}two other doctors of Dusseldorfs\NEisler Memorial Hospital{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as the murder\Nof Adolf Junkers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This news just in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,– A confession? That's impossible.\N{\i1}– According to the police announcement,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to the police announcement,\Non the fourth before dawn,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kenzo Tenma, who had been\Ndenying all accusations until now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has admitted to\Nthe allegations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do\Nto Dr. Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of torture did you subject him\Nin order to extract this false confession?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you get\Nyour hands off of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NLet me see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet him in person and expose\Nwhat happened to him during interrogation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He refused to see me\Nthough I'm his lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that his confession\Nreally was of his own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done some research.\NI know the interrogators.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not the kind of people\Nthat would use torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Tenma confessed\Nwillingly. Astonishingly willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Verdemann, could it be that you also\Nbelieve that Tenma's confession is real?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell his motives\Nunless I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Verdemann speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Baul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry for calling you\Nat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't meet you there because\Nof some urgent business.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How was it?\NWas Dr. Tenma serious?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. He refused to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as we were trying to\Nprove his innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he gives a complete confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that respect,\Nyour father was quite admirable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He never caved in,\Nno matter how harsh his interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He continued to\Nplead his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His innocence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now,\NMr. Verdemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Verdemann?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That woman...\NWhat did you say her name was?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The important witness who could\Nprove Tenma's innocence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is she right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's at a hotel in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No. She's a pretty difficult woman.\NI'll meet with her by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was admirable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up, Miss Heinemann.\NI know you're in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The maid said that\Nshe couldn't make the beds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because you spent the entire day\Nin your room drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Heinemann... I know very well\Nthat you hate Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life would have\Ncontinued to go well
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if your relationship with Tenma\Nhad continued
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,even after you had lost your father,\Nthe hospital director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Dr. Tenma dumped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Dr. Tenma threw\Nyour life into disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was jailed on\Nsuspicions of espionage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time, I was looked upon\Nas the son of a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My father threw\Nmy life into disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't give in. Why?\NWhy do you think I kept on fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believed,\Nmy father was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is innocent.\NMy father is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent... Innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those I believe in\Nmust be innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove Tenma's innocence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma must be innocent!\NJust like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like how my father\Nhad to be innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where you can\Nreach my partner and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please contact us when\Nyou feel like testifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being transported to\Nthe detention center tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only been a few days\Nsince his confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because Tenma's\Nconfession was so willing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we do anything,\NMr. Verdemann?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The police are trying to reason\Nwith Tenma into seeing us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway\Nwhere's Eva Heinemann?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:17:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's probably\Ndrinking at some bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dusseldorf...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all these places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wretched town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been sitting here\Nfor five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was copying down\Na very interesting essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shall we move elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Let's go eat!\NWhere would you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Italian?\NHow about French?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you\Nkeep on writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay there\Nand keep writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm placing stones so the wind\Ndoesn't blow it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.\NWhy are you laying it out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to have lunch out here\Nevery once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's having lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We are. I made sandwiches.\NI hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There are bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all covered in dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a complete disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to\Neat one too, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Verdemann wasn't answering,\Nso I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh. His wife just gave birth,\Nso he's probably at the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've heard rumors about you,\NEva Heinemann.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you like,\Nyou can talk to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Testifying to\NTenma's innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. That's good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...\NWhat hotel are you at?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.59,0:22:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right over.
